<P>CLARISSA; OR THE HISTORY OF A YOUNG LADY. COMPREHENDING THE MOST IMPORTANT CONCERNS OF PRIVATE LIFE. Abridged from the WORKS of SAMUEL RICHARDSON, <ABBR>E&s;q.</ABBR> AUTHOR OF PAMELA, and Sir CHARLES GRANDISON.</P>
